      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-light">Breastfeeding is a learned skill. Prepare yourself now.</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">I know how overwhelming and stressful it can feel as a first-time mom, especially when it comes to
          feeding your baby.</p>
        <ul class="mt-5 list-disc pl-8">
          <li>When do I start feeding?</li>
          <li>How long do I feed?</li>
          <li>Will I get the latch right?</li>
          <li>How do I know my baby is eating enough?</li>
          <li>How often do I feed?</li>
          <li>When do I need to pump?</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-5">But you don't have to figure it out alone!</p>
        <p class="mt-5">By learning the basics ahead of time, you will feel prepared, gain confidence and be excited to feed
          your baby. We can work together and develop a plan that works for you.</p>
        <p class="mt-5">I recommend you book a consultation from 28 weeks onwards so that the information is still fresh.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:gap-12 ">
