      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-light">What to expect at an antenatal breastfeeding session:</h2>
        <ul class="mt-5 list-disc pl-8">
          <li>Understand the breast changes that occur during pregnancy</li>
          <li>Learn how your body produces breastmilk</li>
          <li>Learn how to hand-express colostrum</li>
          <li>Discover the benefits of skin-to-skin contact and your baby's first breastfeed</li>
          <li>Appreciate the importance of the golden hour after birth</li>
          <li>Position your baby effectively at the breast to optimise latch</li>
          <li>Know what to expect in the first few days after birth</li>
          <li>Express and store your breastmilk safely and confidently</li>
          <li>Recognise and manage common breastfeeding challenges in the early weeks</li>
        </ul>
      </ul>
